  <brief_title>Evaluation of Efficacy and Safety of Dapagliflozin as Monotherapy in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Who Have Inadequate Glycaemic Control With Diet and Exercise Alone</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 24-week National Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group, Phase III Trial in India to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Dapagliflozin as Monotherapy in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Who Have Inadequate Glycaemic Control With Diet and Exercise Alone.</official_title>
